      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Snowball\u0027s Chance...",
        "Client": "Hapless Trader",
        "Description": "I absolutely cannot believe how awful\r\nmy luck is. No way that thing could\u0027ve\r\nhit me! There I was...bobbing...weaving.\r\nZigging...zagging. Just when I thought\r\nI had gotten away from this Lagombi\r\n*BAM* me and all my goods crushed\r\nby a snowball. Unbelievable...",
        "Target": "Hunt a Lagombi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Alerte : boules de neige !",
        "Client": "Marchande malchanceuse",
        "Description": "J\u0027en reviens pas d\u0027avoir \u00E9t\u00E9\r\ntouch\u00E9e ! Je g\u00E9rais comme une pro\r\net je pensais avoir \u00E9chapp\u00E9 au\r\nLagombi, quand soudain... BAM ! Une\r\ngrosse boule de neige nous envoie\r\nvaldinguer, mon chariot et moi !\r\nIl y a qu\u0027\u00E0 moi que \u00E7a arrive...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Lagombi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Una palla di neve fortunata",
        "Client": "Mercante sfortunata",
        "Description": "Che sfortuna! Non pu\u00F2 avermi\r\ncolpito. Correvo a zig-zag,\r\nschivavo... E proprio quando\r\npensavo di aver seminato quel\r\nLagombi, una palla di neve\r\nha distrutto tutte le mie\r\nmerci. Incredibile!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Lagombi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schneeballeffekt",
        "Client": "Gl\u00FCcklose H\u00E4ndlerin",
        "Description": "Ich fasse es nicht! Wie konnte\r\ner mich treffen? Ich bin ge-\r\nh\u00FCpft, get\u00E4nzelt, im Zickzack\r\ngelaufen... Als ich dachte,\r\nich sei dem Lagombi entwischt\r\n\u2013 B\u00C4M, trifft ein Schneeball\r\nmich und meine Waren...",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Lagombi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Ojo con las bolas de nieve",
        "Client": "Mercader desafortunada",
        "Description": "\u00A1Pero qu\u00E9 mala suerte tengo!\r\nCuando cre\u00EDa que hab\u00EDa dejado\r\natr\u00E1s a ese Lagombi, va y\r\ndestruye toda mi mercanc\u00EDa\r\nde un bolazo de nieve...\r\nNo gano para disgustos...",
        "Target": "Caza un Lagombi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
